		}]
	}, {
		id: "0000000000003014"
		x: 8.0d
		y: 0.0d
		dependencies: ["000000000000300F"]
		title: "The First Vein"
		icon: {id: "minecraft:iron_ingot", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Go underground. Iron and copper both sit in the upper ore layers — copper near the surface, iron slightly deeper. They share the same mine trip.", "Thirty-two iron ingots covers the material cost for the Tinkers' Smeltery build. Sixteen copper opens your full set of copper parts at the Part Builder. Bring torches and don't surface until you have both.", "The continent above is patient. It will wait."]
		tasks: [{
			id: "0000000000003015"
